title: DoseDiary
description:
Join DoseDiary, the ultimate app for tracking GLP-1 injections, weight loss progress, and health milestones. Register now for early access and optimize your wellness journey.

DoseDiary will support the following GLP-1 medications at launch:
Tirzepatide (Mounjaro® & Zepbound®)
Semaglutide (Ozempic® & Wegovy®)
Liraglutide (Saxenda® & Victoza®)
